-- Ivernia Names Wayne Richardson as CEO; Alan De’ath to Retire
-- B y   S i m o n   C a s e y
-- 2012-12-17T14:36:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-17/ivernia-names-wayne-richardson-as-ceo-alan-de-ath-to-retire.html
Ivernia Inc. (IVW) , owner of the Paroo
Station lead mine in Western Australia, named Wayne Richardson
as chief executive officer to replace Alan De’ath, who is
retiring.  Ivernia, which is based in Toronto, commented today in a
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
